snippet: LEAD: The Southern California Home Financing Authority is tentatively offering $52.8 million in single-family mortgage revenue bonds with a maximum yield of 7.625 percent for an issue due in 2022 through underwriters led by Bear, Stearns & Company...
lead_paragraph: LEAD: The Southern California Home Financing Authority is tentatively offering $52.8 million in single-family mortgage revenue bonds with a maximum yield of 7.625 percent for an issue due in 2022 through underwriters led by Bear, Stearns & Company.
